#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lamps/hemi.rst:34
msgid ""
"These settings are common to most types of lamps, and are described in :doc:"
"`Light Properties </render/blender_render/lighting/lights/lamp_panel>`."
msgstr ""
"Ces réglages sont communs à la plupart des types de lampe, et sont décrits "
"dans les :doc:`Propriétés de lumière </render/blender_render/lighting/lights/"
"lamp_panel>`."

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lamps/hemi.rst:38
msgid "Layer, Negative, Specular, and Diffuse"
msgstr "Layer, Negative, Specular, et Diffuse"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lamps/hemi.rst:37
msgid ""
"These settings control what the lamp affects, as described in :ref:`What "
"Light Affects <bi-lamp-influence>`."
msgstr ""
"Ces réglages contrôlent ce que la lampe affecte, comme décrit dans :ref:`Ce "
"que la lumière affecte <bi-lamp-influence>`."

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lamps/hemi.rst:40
msgid ""
"The *Hemi* lamp has no light falloff settings: it always uses a constant "
"attenuation (i.e. no attenuation)."
msgstr ""
"La lampe *Hemi* n'a pas de réglages de vignettage : elle utilise toujours "
"une atténuation constante (càd pas d'atténuation)."

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lamps/hemi.rst:43
msgid ""
"Since this lamp is the only lamp which cannot cast any shadow, the *Shadow* "
"panel is absent."
msgstr ""
"Puisque cette lampe est la seule lampe qui ne peut pas jeter d'ombre, le "
"panneau *Shadow* est absent."

